{"tid":867092,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"希古恩表示他深感祖雲達斯簽下基斯坦奴朗拿度後將他踢走","createTime":"2018-10-18T11:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T04:55:26.000Z","uid":86090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ae95118bf3f8b6abcfdbe222a3bed976d3d03a7e","tid":867092,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:27:02.000Z","msg":"Gonzalo Higuain claims he was forced out of Juventus to make way for Cristiano Ronaldo<br />\nHiguain joined Juventus from Napoli in 2016 for a then Italian record &euro;90 million fee<br />\n<br />\nGonzalo Higuain claimed he joined AC Milan this summer after being forced out of Juventus to make way for Cristiano Ronaldo.<br />\n<br />\nHiguain controversially joined Juventus from Napoli in 2016 for a then Italian record &euro;90 million fee and scored 55 goals in 105 appearances while claiming successive Serie A titles. <br />\n<br />\nThe Argentinian striker joined Milan on loan in August shortly after Ronaldo's arrival was confirmed.<br />\n<br />\nJuventus fans celebrate Cristiano Ronaldo's arrival in Turin<br />\nJuventus fans celebrate Cristiano Ronaldo's arrival in Turin (Getty)<br />\n&quot;The decision to leave was not mine,&quot; Higuain told Gazzetta dello Sport. &quot;I gave everything for Juventus, I won several titles, after which Cristiano arrived.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The club wanted to make a leap in quality and they told me that I could not stay and that they were trying to find a solution. The best solution was Milan &quot;.<br />\n<br />\nHiguain claimed he felt the rumblings of discontent as early as last May when he was left out of the Juventus side who took on Milan in the Coppa Italia final in May. <br />\n<br />\nGonzalo Higuain and Mattia Caldara are introduced to AC Milan fans<br />\nGonzalo Higuain and Mattia Caldara are introduced to AC Milan fans (Getty)<br />\n&quot;Mine is a feeling of affection because they treated me very well,&quot; he added. &quot;Companions and supporters have given me huge affection. But I did not ask to leave. Basically, everyone says it, they sent me away.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;That day, I had the feeling inside may that maybe something had broken down. And then they signed Ronaldo.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Milan have given me something more after a World Cup which wasn't great. I found what I was looking for.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nHiguain has scored four in his first nine games for Milan, but his new club are languishing in tenth place in the Serie A table under Gennaro Gattuso, already 12 points behind his league-leading former side. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/gonzalo-higuain-cristiano-ronaldo-juventus-ac-milan-serie-a-transfer-a8589906.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Feuropean%2Fgonzalo-higuain-cristiano-ronaldo-juventus-ac-milan-serie-a-transfer-a8589906.html&d=48Q0sfUiPCFtPlwj4gyWotr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=427940b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/gonzalo-higuain-cristiano-ronaldo-juventus-ac-milan-serie-a-transfer-a8589906.html</a>"},{"pid":"4821c5ae851bd95890251454dccc1d148109a73e","tid":867092,"uid":1139,"like":18,"dislike":6,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:28:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f67f8d99562db8717cac54243280897f33fdc99b","tid":867092,"uid":144275,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:30:14.000Z","msg":"斜恩條友係佢腳下甩左幾多個杯走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdda2984f723f24a575d583d2d40b6f0b4fe5eb9","tid":867092,"uid":62815,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"咁咪算睇得起你"},{"pid":"b507747070f96c35c99e593980af497c5f2e2054","tid":867092,"uid":1911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm